  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "NPM dependencies suffer from supply chain attacks. We protect users against those with locked dependencies on repo installs (yarn.lock) + dependabot updates.\r\n\r\n- See https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/3596\r\n\r\nDue to this we should encourage users to only run pre-built docker images since those are guaranteed to install a pre-veted set of safe dependencies.\r\n\r\n**TODO**\r\n\r\n- [x] [Remove instructions to install from npm](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/4115)\r\n- [x] Add warning note to not install from npm",
